  "Clear QR code and learning data": {
   "width": 10140,
   "height": 9780,
   "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Clear QR code and Learning data",
     "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 240,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 9720
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 20.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "ATCU is replaced by new one >> Please use manual request function",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 1080,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 14.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1. Extract QR code from old ATCU using Service $221600",
     "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 1560,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 6840
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2. Replace New one, write QR code using service $2E1600+QR code from old ATCU",
     "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 1920,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 8280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3. Ignition OFF and wait  about 3 seconds",
     "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 2280,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 6840
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CVT is replaced by new one",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 2880,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 10200
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 14.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1. Prepare QR code(The package of CVT includes CD-ROM)",
     "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 3300,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 6840
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2. Erase QR code ($31011802) in below condition",
     "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 3720,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 4080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "R range, Vehicle stopped, Engine stopped, Ignition ON, Accelerator pedal ON",
     "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 720,
      "top": 4200,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 6840
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3. Write QR code from CD-ROM using $2E1600+QR code (use manual request)",
     "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 8160,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 7680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4. Ignition OFF and wait 3 seconds",
     "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 8520,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 6600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5. Replace the CVT, and make ignition ON",
     "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 8880,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 6600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "If QR code is not in EEPROM, self learning flag is displayed as \"self learning NOK\"",
     "color": "rgb(191,255,191)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 6120,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Calibri",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
